<table><td class="body_box2">
<!-- Node: "DOOM 3 spec requirements" -->
<div class="body_box_header">DOOM 3 spec requirements</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Tuesday, July 20, 2004 - 21:27</small><br /><br />
Todd Hollenshead, Id Software CEO, said that DOOM 3 will require:<br />
<i><br />
A 1.5-gigahertz Intel Pentium 4 chip or AMD Athlon 1500.<br />
384 megabytes of memory.<br />
Two gigabytes of hard drive space.<br />
An nVidia GeForce 3 graphics card or better; or an ATI Technologies 8500 or better.</i><br />
<br />
If your pc doesn't meet the spec requirements head over to <a href = "http://www.chron.com/cs/CDA/ssistory.mpl/tech/weekly/2690450">Houston Chronicle</a> to read on how you can improve your pc.
