<div class="body_box_header">Update Finished</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/8" title="View user profile.">Jherax</a> on Saturday, July 17, 2004 - 22:15</small><br /><br />
Applied a few updates tonight, the biggest of which includes major changes to the layout when you are logged in under your user account.<br />
<br />
Logged in users now have the benefit of having only 1 ad appear on screen, as well as a new, modified interface. Since browsing the site with only a single ad is infinitely faster than trying trying to surf with all three of them visible at once, I highly recommend logging in or creating a new user if you haven't yet.<br />
<br />
Oh, and don't forget to leave comments and feedback, we like that kind of stuff around here :)
